<h1>Divide by Zero</h1>
<%= form_tag url_for(:controller => 'divide_by_zero', :action => 'printOut'), :method => 'get' do %>
    <p>
      <%= label_tag "First Variable" %><br>
      <%= number_field_tag :var1 %>
    </p>

    <p>
      <%= label_tag "Divided by" %><br>
      <%= number_field_tag :var2 %>
    </p>

    <p>
      <%= submit_tag "Submit" %><br/>
    </p>

	<% end %>
<br/>
<br/>
<h3>About</h3>
<p>When divided by 0 value, the begin-rescue command will catch the exception and print the error trance through a web browser.</p>
